text: Hey everyone! I’m curious if anyone else is doing content syndication (email blasts) right now and seeing less than expected results? We have done 3 in the last couple of weeks and seen pretty bad results…which could be a sign of the current times but I wanted to see if anyone else is having a similar experience? Thanks!
